B040C016V019	40	16	19	And I will give you the keys of the kingdom of heaven, and whatever you bind on the earth will have been bound in heaven, and whatever you loose on the earth will have been loosed in heaven."
B040C016V020	40	16	20	Then He commanded His disciples that they should tell no one that He was Jesus the Christ.
