B040C018V035	40	18	35	Thus also My heavenly Father will do to you, if you do not forgive each [one] his brother their trespasses, from your hearts."
B040C019V001	40	19	1	Now it came to pass, when Jesus had finished these words, that He with from Galilee and went to the region of Judea beyond the Jordan.
B040C019V002	40	19	2	And great crowds followed Him, and He healed them there.
