B040C019V005	40	19	5	and He said, 'For this reason a man shall leave his father and mother and shall be joined to his wife, and the two shall become one flesh'?
B040C019V006	40	19	6	So then, they are no longer two but one flesh. Therefore what God has joined together, let not man separate."
