B040C019V026	40	19	26	And looking on [them], Jesus said to them, "With men this is impossible, but with God all things are possible."
B040C019V027	40	19	27	Then Peter answered and said to Him, "See, we have left all and followed You. What then shall we have?"
B040C019V028	40	19	28	So Jesus said to them, "Assuredly I say to you, that in the Regeneration, when the Son of Man sits on His glorious throne, you who have followed Me will also sit on twelve thrones, judging the twelve tribes of Israel.
