B042C007V042	42	7	42	And when they had nothing with which to pay back, he freely forgave them both. Tell [Me], therefore, which of them will love him more?"
B042C007V043	42	7	43	Simon answered and said, "I suppose [it is the one] to whom he forgave more."And He said to him, "You have judged correctly."
B042C007V044	42	7	44	And turning to the woman, He said to Simon, "Do you see this woman? I entered into your house; you gave Me no water for My feet, but this [woman] has washed My feet with her tears and wiped them with the hair of her head.
B042C007V045	42	7	45	You gave Me no kiss, but this [woman] has not stopped kissing My feet since the time I came in.
B042C007V046	42	7	46	You did not anoint My head with oil, but this [woman] has anointed My feet with perfume.
B042C007V047	42	7	47	For which reason I say to you, her many sins have been forgiven, because she loved much. But to whom little is forgiven, the same loves little."
