B042C017V030	42	17	30	In the same way it shall be in the day when the Son of Man is revealed.
B042C017V031	42	17	31	In that day, [he] who shall be on the housetop, and his goods in the house, let him not come down to take them away. And likewise he who is in the field, let him not turn back for the things[ left] behind.
