B042C018V030	42	18	30	who shall not receive many times more in this present time, and in the age to come eternal life."
B042C018V031	42	18	31	Then taking the twelve aside, He said to them, "Behold, we are going up to Jerusalem, and all things that are written by the prophets concerning the Son of Man will be accomplished.
