B045C012V008	45	12	8	whether exhorting, in the exhortation; whether sharing, with simplicity; whether leading, with diligence; whether showing mercy, with cheerfulness.
B045C012V009	45	12	9	[Let] love [be] without hypocrisy. Abhor that which is evil. Cling to that which is good.
